Echo \*
Just return * 

Echo « * »
Return * 

Echo
displaying lines of text or string which are passed as arguments on the command line 

Echo */*
Display all the repositories and their path (Alex/Wrap anaelle/747art.txt anaelle/art/txt etc...)

Rm *
